Name: Alzamend Neuro Inc
Description: Alzamend Neuro Inc. is a biotechnology firm dedicated to the development of innovative therapies for neurodegenerative diseases, particularly Alzheimer's disease. As it progresses its therapeutic candidates through clinical trials, the firm remains committed to improving patient quality of life and addressing critical health challenges.
